snippet.title: Isle Goblin Overview Trailer - Sandbox Townbuilding RPG
snippet.description:
Hello everyone! I needed a video to post on Steam, so I made this one. Unfortunately I still don't have an official release date for the demo or the early access listing of the game, but I'm working on it as hard as I can. 

If you're new here, welcome! You can join our discord here where I'm happy to answer any questions: 
https://discord.gg/TM8n7ENJPa

You can wishlist the game here: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1688640/Cleanup_on_Isle_Goblin/

Or you can check out the website and get all the links from here: 
https://kilowattgames.com/
